---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Dr. Colin MacLeod ND naturopathic practice. Learn how we collect, use and protect your personal and health information."
  focusKeyword="privacy policy naturopathic doctor Halifax"
>
  <HeroSection title="Privacy Policy" centered>
    Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use and protect your personal information.
  </HeroSection>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-12">Last updated: January 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-12">

          <!-- Introduction -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">Introduction</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
              Dr. Colin MacLeod ND ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy and the confidentiality of your personal health information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose and safeguard your information when you visit our website, use our services or communicate with our practice.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
              We comply with the <strong>Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA)</strong> and applicable provincial health privacy legislation in Nova Scotia.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Information We Collect -->
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">Information We Collect</h2>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800">Personal Information</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-1">
                <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Contact Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, mailing address</li>
                <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Health Information:</strong> Medical history, symptoms, treatment records, lab results and other health-related information necessary for your care</li>
                <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Appointment Information:</strong> Booking details, appointment history and scheduling preferences</li>
                <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Payment Information:</strong> Billing details and insurance information for processing payments</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800">Website Data</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">When you visit our website, we automatically collect:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-1">
                <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent on pages and navigation patterns</li>
                <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Device Information:</strong> Browser type, operating system and IP address</li>
                <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Cookies:</strong> Small data files stored on your device to improve your experience</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- How We Use Your Information -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">We use your personal information to:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1">
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Provide naturopathic medical care and treatment</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Schedule and manage appointments</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Process payments and insurance claims</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Communicate with you about your care, appointments and health information</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Respond to your inquiries and contact form submissions</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Improve our website and services</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Comply with legal and regulatory requirements</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- How We Protect Your Information -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">How We Protect Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
              We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal and health information, including:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-1">
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Secure, encrypted communication channels</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Password-protected electronic health records</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Physical security measures for paper records</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Staff training on privacy and confidentiality</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default">Regular review of our security practices</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Disclosure of Information -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">Disclosure of Information</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">We do not sell, trade or rent your personal information. We may disclose your information only in the following circumstances:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1">
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">With Your Consent:</strong> When you authorize us to share information with other healthcare providers</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">For Treatment:</strong> To other healthcare professionals involved in your care, with your knowledge</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Service Providers:</strong> To trusted third parties who assist us in operating our practice (e.g., appointment booking system, payment processors)</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law, regulation or legal process</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Emergency Situations:</strong> To protect your health or safety, or the health and safety of others</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Third-Party Services -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Our website and practice use the following third-party services:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1">
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Jane App:</strong> Our online booking system. Jane App has its own privacy policy governing how appointment and patient information is handled.</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Google Analytics:</strong> We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our website. This service collects anonymized data about your browsing behavior. You can opt out by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-800 underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Formspree:</strong> Our contact form submissions are processed through Formspree. Your form data is transmitted securely and not stored longer than necessary.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Your Rights -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Under PIPEDA and applicable privacy legislation, you have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1">
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal information we hold</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete information</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Withdrawal of Consent:</strong> Withdraw your consent to certain uses of your information (though this may affect our ability to provide services)</li>
              <li class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors duration-200 text-slate-700 cursor-default"><strong class="text-emerald-800">Complaint:</strong> File a complaint with the Office of the Privacy Commissioner of Canada if you believe your privacy rights have been violated</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Retention of Information -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">Retention of Information</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
              We retain your personal and health information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, and as required by applicable laws and professional regulations. In Nova Scotia, medical records are typically retained for a minimum of 10 years after your last visit or longer for certain types of records.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Children's Privacy -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
              Our website is not intended for children under 16 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children online. For patients under 18, we obtain consent from a parent or guardian.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Changes to This Policy -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
              We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact Us -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-900">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
              If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, wish to exercise your privacy rights or have concerns about how your information is handled, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-emerald-100/70 transition-colors duration-200">
              <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-900">Dr. Colin MacLeod ND</p>
              <p class="text-slate-700">Optimal Wellbeing Clinic</p>
              <p class="text-slate-700">6140 Young Street</p>
              <p class="text-slate-700">Halifax, NS B3K 0G2</p>
              <p class="text-slate-700 mt-3">
                <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+19024064424" class="text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-800">(902) 406-4424</a>
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-6">
              For complaints about privacy practices, you may also contact the Office of the Privacy Commissioner of Canada at <a href="https://www.priv.gc.ca" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-800 underline">www.priv.gc.ca</a>.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
